{"tid":1232032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣做野］宣揚一句 *林鄭企硬不撤回*","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:08:55.000Z","uid":60231,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb529056713bf09590c73c50289347fd55eb699b","tid":1232032,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"政府又想出軟招：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">考慮到社會有強烈不同的意見，</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府已停止立法會大會對修訂《逃犯條例》的工作</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: small;\">希望藉此可讓社會盡快回復平靜和避免任何人受到傷害。政府重申並無重啟程序的時間表。</span><br />\n<br />\n之後政府pr好大機會執住e句野矇混過關，得大家 誤以為 停止=撤回，仲好可能係cctvb既重點重複語句，去呃d易動搖唔識針著字眼既人，<br />\n目的：<br />\n令人軟化，減弱民意<br />\n<br />\n記住：停止不是撤回<br />\n<br />\n我地要一句直接清晰易記既tagline, <br />\n所以請文宣無論喺digital定print ad, 至少短期內都要highlight: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林鄭企硬不撤回</span></span> 用紅色超大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae37c5a15c20d17c2f221adb71d6134bf153e6ad","tid":1232032,"uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:23:58.000Z","msg":"係, 唔可以比任何掩飾機會比政府"},{"pid":"c1bdda52a7beab9cee05b50dcdb3663accc2d574","tid":1232032,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:24:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56b093b6a056bbb597ff7989c43e5b398fa9c119","tid":1232032,"uid":91721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">太古烈士梁凌杰遺願</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全面撤回送中<br />\n我們不是暴動<br />\n釋放學生傷者<br />\n林鄭下台</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"ce0d46de01fb1b31783a4